{"tid":387647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通訊局用引導性提問進行調查 為放寬植入式廣告鋪路","createTime":"2017-09-04T19:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T23:25:14.000Z","uid":127728,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75cc6a9925de2244b6d6d28396c03f93b50a6f6d","tid":387647,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>通訊局擬放寬植入式廣告</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/finance/html/2017/09/20170904_180723.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Ffinance%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F09%2F20170904_180723.shtml&d=BRPl2014VxdLa%2FPZV5rGyf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=60ac8863\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/finance/html/2017/09/20170904_180723.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n通訊事務管理局公布，決定檢討業務守則中規管植入式廣告的相關條文，務求在可行和適當情況下，放寬現行規管制度。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局去年中，就海外規管免費電視服務的植入式廣告進行研究，結果顯示香港規管的基本原則與海外主要地區相若， 但認為現行規定有放寬空間。<br />\n<br />\n該局今年2月至6月又進行意見調查，訪問逾1,500人；並於7月舉辦六場專題小組討論會，參加者包括公眾人士、電視及電台廣播諮詢計劃成員、創意產業和媒體專業人員。<br />\n<br />\n收集所得的意見顯示，香港觀眾普遍對免費電視節目出現植入式廣告不覺得反感，但有需要規管。觀眾的接受程度主要視乎廣告表達手法是否自然以及有否影響觀賞趣味。<br />\n<br />\n此外，觀眾和業界都傾向支持放寬規定，以提升免費電視服務的競爭力，促進業界整體發展。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局考慮有關意見後，認為有理據就條文展開檢討，將着手進行修訂，並會邀請持牌機構參與，並諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我真係去睇下通訊局份調查報告啦，點知發現原來通訊局已經 set 左 agenda，用引導性問題令受訪者接受放寬規管植入式廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見調查的報告摘要：<a href=\"http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_1076/ESc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_1076%2FESc.pdf&d=BRPl2014VxdLa%2FPZV5rGyf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=59ac7e14\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_1076/ESc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>使用植入式廣告</strong><br />\n3.3.17 當被問及在近年新媒體相繼出現，免費電視台所面對的競爭越來越大的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前提</span></span>下，是否接受免費電視台增加節目內出現植入式廣告以增加收入時，超過半數觀眾（56.6%）表示接受，18.2%表示不接受，19.7%則表示「一半半／視乎情況」<br />\n<br />\n3.3.19 觀眾被問及<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果</span></span>讓免費電視台<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">增加廣告以增加收入</span></span>，對不同廣告宣傳模式的接受程度。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>免費電視廣告</strong><br />\n3.3.2 與免費電視於黃金時段內播放的廣告數量相比，認為於非黃金時段內播放的廣告數量「適中」的觀眾比率較高，達71.8%（對比2014年調查74.9%；2009年調查模擬／同步數碼頻道70.4%及其他數碼頻道71.3%），18.8%則認為非黃金時段的廣告數量「太多」或「多了少許」（對比2014年調查16.0%；2009年調查模擬／同步數碼頻道16.3%及其他數碼頻道9.9%）。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極少</span>觀眾（0.7%）表示接受「可以增加多一點」或「可以增加少許」廣告</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b7e34013e43a56eb14d0e050d25947e197a323","tid":387647,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T20:03:46.000Z","msg":"港共不意外"},{"pid":"02c6acf84766b5a681d263dcd3909e5c2a28170e","tid":387647,"uid":43976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T20:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029a5b5fd4c7c185e4a7cb383d3990d122bb7eab","tid":387647,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T20:26:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58a12991a03786170557139ac039188e4fa151f6","tid":387647,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T20:34:44.000Z","msg":"民眾喜迎油價上升.jpg"},{"pid":"d6dbd05585ee19b48532ef91447d92b3905056c6","tid":387647,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T20:53:56.000Z","msg":"TVB就死想起死回生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfefa1ed6ac5df6c0203c0a2935c0b0991400f69","tid":387647,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T22:55:14.000Z","msg":"越多廣告咪越趕客。"},{"pid":"de46be970920003a3bc0cbb28245d4b82bc9165e","tid":387647,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:01:28.000Z","msg":"改黎把撚咩 橫掂都係罰雞碎咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b97acfdec9f06de3ae327bf6b61837f75803fa","tid":387647,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:09:08.000Z","msg":"對市民好既就收緊自我審查 對商家佬有益既就放寬"},{"pid":"a2ba9d84465757e8f743604834ac49f0aa394cc2","tid":387647,"uid":76323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:17:52.000Z","msg":"屌你通訊局 當年唔發牌俾wiki 搞到電視質素越黎越下降"},{"pid":"7c59a7658429e798ce8be9df5f0115454b4495c6","tid":387647,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:20:24.000Z","msg":"以後日日都愛回家～食炸雞<br />\n<br />\n蕭正楠直頭開鉅記"},{"pid":"66a69710d23b9ce1b7757117bc1ae9b12b7b9485","tid":387647,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:25:14.000Z","msg":"想佢死真係靠呢劑,以佢哋一貫做法,即係原本己經難睇嘅節目再加埋肉酸<br />\n成個台都冇大卡士夠膽死想人忍埋擺明植入廣告,創作肯定因為遷就廣告更焗限<br />\n外景例要拍埋廣告商店舖同用章節賣膏藥,仲要係由一堆三打七去做😏<br />\n屋企人已經有轉台睇,情願佢哋直頭睇大陸台,起碼唔係三日唔埋兩日用停車場景"}]}